### Auth Overview:

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/overview HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Register

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
