### OAuth Google Start

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google/start HTTP/1.1


### OAuth Google Callback (manual test)

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google/callback?code={{code}}&state={{state}} HTTP/1.1


### Get profile

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get User By ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/users/1ff3a099-fb67-44b3-849c-8b0af14e7960 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get All Users

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Change Password

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/password/change HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "confirmPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "oldPassword": "Ol@123456"
}
